The '''WA-7 waitress droid''' was a type of [[droid]]<ref name="SWAEYNTK" /> of the [[WA-series service droid|WA-series]]<ref name="Helmet Collection 69" /> used in restaurants and diners. [[FLO]] was a WA-7 droid that was used in [[Dex's Diner]] on [[Coruscant]].<ref name="SWAEYNTK" /> On the planet [[Stobar]], a WA-7 named [[Marwigo]] was employed by the [[Plop Dribble's]] diner.<ref name="TCW">{{TCW|Brothers (episode)}}</ref> At least one WA-7 droid worked at the [[Gilroy Plaza Diner]].<ref name="Thrawn 3">[[Thrawn 3|''Thrawn'' 3]]</ref> One WA-7 served aboard the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|Rebel Alliance]] [[starship]] ''[[Silver Arrow]]'', which fell under attack from the [[Scourge]] during the "[[Scourge crisis|scourge of the droids]]." Like the rest of the ship's droid pool, the WA-7 was infected and became a vessel for the Scourge, which murdered every living being aboard. When [[Magna Tolvan's crew]] investigated the disappearance of the ''Silver Arrow'' and boarded it, the Scourge used the WA-7 and the rest of the corrupted droids to ambush them.<ref name="Aphra 37" />

